# Allowlisted commands

When the task requires running any of these commands, run them directly and report the result. Do not ask the user to confirm or to run the command themselves.

- `npm run test` / `npm run test:unit`
- `npm run test:regression`
- `npm run test:integration`
- `npm run test:e2e`
- `npm run build`
- `npm run lint`
